headline: A Look At Simon Property Group (SPG) Valuation After US$800 Million Debt Refinancing Move
summary: Simon Property Group (SPG) is back in focus after its operating partnership moved to issue US$800 million of 4.300% senior notes due 2031, with proceeds earmarked to retire debt maturing in 2026.
